# Normalize SQL line endings to LF in the repository.
# This guards against the CRLF/LF checksum-mismatch class of bugs (sqlx issue #2659,
# Codex Desktop incident 2025) where Windows checkouts produce CRLF-hashed migration
# state that diverges from LF-hashed binaries after an app update.
# The CRLF→LF normalization in migrator.ts is a runtime backstop; this is the source gate.
*.sql text eol=lf
